snippet.title: Ace Entertainment
snippet.description:
ACE Entertainment distributes Series, Mini-Series, Tv Movies, Documentaries and 3D content for all medias (Tv, Video, VOD, Internet, Apps.) in French speaking Europe.

ACE Entertainment also develops iPhone, iPad and Android Apps, as well as supplying mobile content to Telecom Operators and Distribution Channels worldwide for handless devices.

ACE Entertainment is part of the SJ Investments group, specialized in investing in the audiovisual industry.

Jerome Reygner-Kalfon, Managing Partner, started as a Sale Assistant at Europe Images International (Lagardere Group). Then moved to AB International Distribution (AB Group) as a Sales Manager then as the Sales Director. After 4 years he decided to launch ACE Entertainment with Sebastien Semon in 2003.

Sebastien Semon, Managing Partner, started in the finance industry before moving into the TV business (AB Group) as a Multimedia Director during 2 years then started ACE Entertainment with Jerome Reygner-Kalfon.
